Android Api嘅seekTo method係Keyframe-base，你唔會有得逐個frame咁掃。<br />\n我只係見過d custom嘅frame accurate seeking demo，但搵唔到個可以日常用video player。<br />\n<br />\nMXPlayer個seeking好似最正常，有得一路掃一路preview，但每格可能都唔止一秒。<br />\n<br />\nVLC 個video setting有得熄 &quot;fast seek&quot;，但冇即時preview，掃緊嗰時得個秒數睇，而且只係準確至一秒，要跟準確timestamp又唔得，要睇畫面掃又唔得。<br />\n<br />\n我冇用iphone，但有用mac，個原裝player用trackpad seek真係又順又準，mac版vlc都係唔得"},{"pid":"eaa65a8f40a3fcad3b44db0f2edc63967cae37c2","tid":1003401,"uid":42064,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:18:19.000Z","msg":"一段24鐘鐘嘅片，mx player 掃，見住佢秒數郁左4-5秒，畫面先郁一格。<br />\n<br />\n9秒嘅片，就一秒一格。<br />\n<br />\n當初寫media view嗰時以當時cpu效能去諗，諗住快就得，之後冇改過呢part。<br />\n<br />\n你search Android exact seek或者precise seeking就睇到，有d人話自己有個exact seek嘅demo，但冇公開製成品，有個放左demo上playstore，但始終只係demo，超難用，而且seek完係要load幾秒 (我已經pixel3試)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=at.aau.itec.android.mediaplayerdemo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dat.aau.itec.android.mediaplayerdemo&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FUwFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=54a2b524\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=at.aau.itec.android.mediaplayerdemo</a>"},{"pid":"2ed72dc4cb7dd2d78c4b099b279d66eb53628513","tid":1003401,"uid":191815,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"估唔到有人咁認真咁答<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上面以為串下iPhone就好威威，乜都冇答過仲以為自己好醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0faa6bc6712c04922bb52a60048a611b9e0ebd5c","tid":1003401,"uid":1826,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2ed72dc4cb7dd2d78c4b099b279d66eb53628513","tid":1003401,"uid":191815,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T02:31:40.000Z